1.What is Sell-Scripting?
2.How to write a Shell-Script?
3.Importance of She-Bang?
4. How to run our scripts from Anywhere??
Ans) 1.session-level
     export PATH=$PATH:/root/git/
     2.user-level
     #vi .bashrc
     export PATH=$PATH:/root/git/
     :wq!
     3.System-level
     #vi /etc/profiles
     export PATH=$PATH:/root/git/
     :wq!
